{"tid":2199942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關注台灣]美副國務卿凱克拉奇下周訪台 主持經濟對話","createTime":"2020-09-12T14:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T06:07:35.000Z","uid":294518,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"428ec55e865d6884455119c705c86b63285d5cf3","tid":2199942,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"美副國務卿凱克拉奇下周訪台 主持經濟對話<br />\n繼上個月初美國衛生與公共服務部長阿扎爾高調訪台後，台灣媒體昨天報道稱美國副國務卿凱克拉奇（Keith Krach）將於本月17日至19日訪台，主持「台美經濟與商業對話」（US-Taiwan Economic and Commercial Dialogue）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.snowflake.com/resource/cloud-data-warehousing-dummies/?_bt=442987505932&amp;_bk=&amp;_bm=&amp;_bn=d&amp;_bg=105133106834&amp;utm_medium=search&amp;utm_source=adwords&amp;utm_campaign=NA%20-%20Display%20-%20Prospecting%20-%20DW%20for%20Dummies&amp;utm_adgroup=NA%20-%20Display%20-%20Prospecting%20-%20Similar%20to%20Converters%20-%20DW%20for%20Dummies&amp;utm_term=&amp;utm_region=na&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI9df3-Ovj6wIVChhiCh21AwRDEAEYASAAEgLVz_D_BwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.snowflake.com%2Fresource%2Fcloud-data-warehousing-dummies%2F%3F_bt%3D442987505932%26_bk%3D%26_bm%3D%26_bn%3Dd%26_bg%3D105133106834%26utm_medium%3Dsearch%26utm_source%3Dadwords%26utm_campaign%3DNA%2520-%2520Display%2520-%2520Prospecting%2520-%2520DW%2520for%2520Dummies%26utm_adgroup%3DNA%2520-%2520Display%2520-%2520Prospecting%2520-%2520Similar%2520to%2520Converters%2520-%2520DW%2520for%2520Dummies%26utm_term%3D%26utm_region%3Dna%26gclid%3DEAIaIQobChMI9df3-Ovj6wIVChhiCh21AwRDEAEYASAAEgLVz_D_BwE&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9fxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=243f7bda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.snowflake.com/resource/cloud-data-warehousing-dummies/?_bt=442987505932&amp;_bk=&amp;_bm=&amp;_bn=d&amp;_bg=105133106834&amp;utm_medium=search&amp;utm_source=adwords&amp;utm_campaign=NA%20-%20Display%20-%20Prospecting%20-%20DW%20for%20Dummies&amp;utm_adgroup=NA%20-%20Display%20-%20Prospecting%20-%20Similar%20to%20C